Class Gui

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • Gui
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class Gui
extends javafx.application.Application
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable
    Gui is a class that creates the GUI for the user. It also reads in a text file of baseball players and inserts them into an array and lets the user create their own list of baseball players.

    1.8
